snippet.title: Phantom Line - Reveal Trailer - Join the paranormal SWAT
snippet.description:
PLAYTEST - early co-op horror shooter: https://discord.com/invite/uHheyk2PBA 

STEAM - add to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2400840

TWITTER/X - Follow the channel to read about latest paranormal leaks: https://x.com/AntistaticTeam

Phantom Line is a co-op (1-4) shooter set in the post-nuclear European continent. Your mission is to search and contain paranormal events and activities (anomalies) hidden from the public eye, in an open world map full of dynamic events.

Learn more at: https://antistatic-studios.com/
